Nayagam S(1), Conteh L(2), Sicuri E(3), Shimakawa Y(4), Suso P(5), Tamba S(5), 
Njie R(6), Njai H(5), Lemoine M(7), Hallett TB(8), Thursz M(9).

Author information:
(1)Division of Digestive Diseases, St Mary's Hospital, Imperial College, London, 
UK; Department of Infectious Disease Epidemiology, School of Public Health, 
