Sensitivity of imatinib-resistant T315I BCR-ABL CML to a synergistic combination 
of ponatinib and forskolin treatment.

Oaxaca DM(1), Yang-Reid SA(1), Ross JA(1), Rodriguez G(1), Staniswalis JG(2), 
